OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright spells will be
OL,6,Finterspersed with the occasional
OL,7,Fshower through the morning and into
OL,8,Fthe early afternoon. Cloud will
OL,9,Fincrease as outbreaks of rain spread
OL,10,Fnorth through the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe evening begins cloudy
OL,13,Fwith outbreaks of showery rain. Drier
OL,14,Fconditions return for a time from the
OL,15,Flate evening. Low cloud and further
OL,16,Foutbreaks of rain spread north towards
OL,17,Fmorning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
