OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FThe morning will be cloudy
OL,6,Fwith outbreaks of rain, this heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes. The rain will clear to sunny
OL,8,Fspells and showers in the afternoon.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,11,Fover Orkney for a time Saturday
OL,12,Fotherwise Saturday and Sunday stay
OL,13,Fmostly dry and bright. Cloud and
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain, heavy at times,
OL,15,Fspread east Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
